== logs/experiment_oversight_3564067.err ==
- `3563089_1`: about `555/1500`
- `3563089_2`: about `31/1500`, expected slow prompts64 pace

Found one missing final actor with no live retry: `rl_grpo_merge_ablate_prompts8_rollouts64_seed3408`. Its old task `3557214_22` timed out after reaching about step `553/1500`, so I added it to the catch-up manifest and submitted chained continuation waves:

- `3564074 -> 3564075 -> 3564076`
- `3564074_12` is running
- `3564075_12` and `3564076_12` are dependency-held

Updated pass@k job `3561188` to wait for the existing recovery waves plus the new ones.

